    • locateEntityDescriptor

      @Deprecated(forRemoval=true, since="7") EntityPersister locateEntityDescriptor(Class<?> byClass)
      Deprecated, for removal: This API element is subject to removal in a future version.
      No longer used
      Locate an entity mapping descriptor by Class. The passed Class might refer to either the entity Class directly, or it might name a proxy interface for the entity. This method accounts for both, preferring the direct entity name.
      Throws:
      UnknownEntityTypeException - If a matching EntityPersister cannot be located
